---
import ToolShell from '../../components/ToolShell.astro';
---
<ToolShell title="Ecommerce channel budget planner" metaTitle="Free Ecommerce Marketing Budget Planner" eyebrow="Growth planning" description="Work backwards from a monthly revenue target to the orders, sessions and media budget required, then model an indicative channel allocation.">
  <div slot="hero-card" class="hero-plan"><span>Work backwards</span><strong>Target → orders → sessions → spend</strong><p>A budget becomes useful when its traffic, conversion and margin assumptions are visible.</p></div>
  <div slot="tool" class="tool-card">
    <div class="tool-heading"><span>Monthly scenario</span><h2>Build the demand model</h2><p>Use a realistic conversion rate and cost per click for the traffic you plan to buy.</p></div>
    <form class="form-stack" id="budget-planner">
      <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="target-revenue">Target net revenue</label><div class="input-prefix"><span>£</span><input id="target-revenue" name="targetRevenue" type="number" min="1" step="1" value="150000" required /></div></div><div class="field"><label for="planner-aov">Average order value</label><div class="input-prefix"><span>£</span><input id="planner-aov" name="aov" type="number" min="1" step="1" value="80" required /></div></div></div>
      <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="conversion-rate">Expected site conversion rate</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="conversion-rate" name="conversionRate" type="number" min=".1" max="30" step=".1" value="2.5" required /><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label for="avg-cpc">Expected blended cost per click</label><div class="input-prefix"><span>£</span><input id="avg-cpc" name="cpc" type="number" min=".01" step=".01" value="1.20" required /></div></div></div>
      <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="gross-margin">Gross margin available before marketing</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="gross-margin" name="grossMargin" type="number" min="1" max="95" step=".5" value="48" required /><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label for="planner-profit">Target profit margin after marketing</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="planner-profit" name="profitMargin" type="number" min="0" max="50" step=".5" value="10" required /><span>%</span></div></div></div>
      <fieldset class="allocation"><legend>Indicative channel weighting</legend><p>These percentages are normalised automatically. They are a planning view, not a recommendation.</p><div class="allocation-grid"><div class="field"><label for="google-weight">Google</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="google-weight" name="google" type="number" min="0" value="45" /><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label for="meta-weight">Meta</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="meta-weight" name="meta" type="number" min="0" value="35" /><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label for="affiliate-weight">Affiliate</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="affiliate-weight" name="affiliate" type="number" min="0" value="10" /><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label for="retention-weight">Retention</label><div class="input-suffix"><input id="retention-weight" name="retention" type="number" min="0" value="10" /><span>%</span></div></div></div></fieldset>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Build budget scenario</button>
    </form>
    <div class="result-panel" id="budget-results" aria-live="polite"><div class="result-head"><span>Planning output</span><h2 id="budget-status">Scenario ready</h2></div><div class="funnel"><div><strong id="orders-needed">—</strong><span>Orders needed</span></div><i>→</i><div><strong id="sessions-needed">—</strong><span>Sessions needed</span></div><i>→</i><div><strong id="estimated-spend">—</strong><span>Estimated media spend</span></div></div><div class="result-grid"><div class="result-item"><strong id="required-roas">—</strong><span>Required ROAS</span></div><div class="result-item"><strong id="max-spend">—</strong><span>Maximum spend at target margin</span></div></div><div class="channel-output" id="channel-output"></div><div class="planner-action"><div><strong id="planner-action-title">Validate the assumptions before committing spend.</strong><p id="planner-action-copy">Small changes in conversion rate and CPC can materially change the required budget.</p></div><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-arrow">Review the scenario</a></div><p class="disclaimer">Planning estimate only. The model treats all sessions, orders and revenue as equal and does not account for attribution overlap, organic demand, repeat purchase, refunds, tax or channel-specific conversion rates.</p></div>
  </div>
  <h2>Why work backwards from the target?</h2><p>A revenue goal is not an advertising budget. It implies a number of orders, which implies a number of sessions at the expected conversion rate. Paid traffic then has to be available at a cost the gross margin can support.</p>
  <h2>Stress-test three assumptions</h2><ul><li><strong>Conversion rate:</strong> use the rate for comparable paid landing traffic, not the store-wide headline if they differ.</li><li><strong>CPC:</strong> use a blended forecast informed by the intended geography, product and channel.</li><li><strong>Gross margin:</strong> deduct the costs that increase with each order before deciding what is available for acquisition.</li></ul>
  <h2>Channel allocation is not one universal percentage</h2><p>Google, Meta, affiliate and retention channels play different roles. Allocate budget from the available demand, creative capacity, partner opportunity and customer lifecycle—not a generic benchmark.</p>
</ToolShell>
<script>
  const budgetForm = document.getElementById('budget-planner');
  const formatMoney = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-GB',{style:'currency',currency:'GBP',maximumFractionDigits:0});
  const formatInt = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-GB',{maximumFractionDigits:0});
  budgetForm?.addEventListener('submit', event => {
    event.preventDefault();
    const data = new FormData(budgetForm);
    const value = name => Number(data.get(name));
    const revenue=value('targetRevenue'), aov=value('aov'), cvr=value('conversionRate')/100, cpc=value('cpc');
    const gross=value('grossMargin')/100, profit=value('profitMargin')/100;
    const orders=Math.ceil(revenue/aov), sessions=Math.ceil(orders/cvr), spend=sessions*cpc;
    const roas=revenue/spend, maximum=revenue*(gross-profit);
    const viable=maximum>=spend;
    const weights={Google:value('google'),Meta:value('meta'),Affiliate:value('affiliate'),Retention:value('retention')};
    const total=Object.values(weights).reduce((sum,item)=>sum+item,0)||1;
    document.getElementById('orders-needed').textContent=formatInt.format(orders);
    document.getElementById('sessions-needed').textContent=formatInt.format(sessions);
    document.getElementById('estimated-spend').textContent=formatMoney.format(spend);
    document.getElementById('required-roas').textContent=`${roas.toFixed(2)}×`;
    document.getElementById('max-spend').textContent=formatMoney.format(maximum);
    document.getElementById('budget-status').textContent=viable?'The model fits inside the margin guardrail':'The traffic model exceeds the margin guardrail';
    document.getElementById('planner-action-title').textContent=viable?'There is theoretical room inside the target margin.':'At these assumptions, the target is not commercially viable.';
    document.getElementById('planner-action-copy').textContent=viable?`The model leaves approximately ${formatMoney.format(maximum-spend)} of headroom, before unmodelled costs.`:'Improve conversion, reduce CPC, raise margin or revise the target before allocating this spend.';
    document.getElementById('channel-output').innerHTML=Object.entries(weights).map(([name,weight])=>{const share=weight/total;return `<div><span><strong>${name}</strong><small>${(share*100).toFixed(0)}% normalised</small></span><b>${formatMoney.format(spend*share)}</b><i><em style="width:${share*100}%"></em></i></div>`}).join('');
    const result=document.getElementById('budget-results');result.classList.add('active');result.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});
    window.trackSpiresEvent?.('tool_complete',{tool_name:'channel_budget_planner',result_type:viable?'viable':'not_viable'});
  });
</script>
<style>
  .hero-plan>span,.tool-heading>span{color:#91eadb;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase}.hero-plan strong{display:block;margin:.8rem 0;color:white;font-size:1.4rem}.hero-plan p{color:#cbd2df;font-size:.78rem}.tool-heading{margin-bottom:1.5rem}.tool-heading>span{color:var(--violet-dark)}.tool-heading h2{margin:.3rem 0}.tool-heading p{color:var(--slate);font-size:.82rem}.input-prefix,.input-suffix{display:flex;align-items:center;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #cfd5df;border-radius:9px;background:white}.input-prefix span,.input-suffix span{padding:0 .7rem;color:var(--slate);font-weight:700}.input-prefix input,.input-suffix input{border:0!important;border-radius:0!important;outline:0!important}.input-suffix input{text-align:right}.allocation{padding:1rem;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)}.allocation legend{padding:0 .3rem;color:var(--ink);font-weight:800}.allocation>p{margin-bottom:1rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.7rem}.allocation-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:.7rem}.result-panel{background:#effbf8}.result-head>span{color:var(--success);font-size:.67rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase}.result-head h2{margin:.3rem 0 1rem;font-size:1.6rem}.funnel{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;gap:.6rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem}.funnel>div{padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;background:white}.funnel strong,.funnel span{display:block}.funnel strong{color:var(--ink);font-size:1.3rem}.funnel span{color:var(--muted);font-size:.62rem}.funnel i{color:var(--success);font-style:normal}.channel-output{display:grid;gap:.55rem;margin:1rem 0}.channel-output>div{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:.3rem 1rem;padding:.8rem;border-radius:9px;background:white}.channel-output span strong,.channel-output span small{display:block}.channel-output small{color:var(--muted)}.channel-output b{color:var(--ink)}.channel-output i{grid-column:1/-1;height:6px;overflow:hidden;border-radius:999px;background:#e7ebf0}.channel-output em{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:999px;background:var(--mint)}.planner-action{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;align-items:center;padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;background:var(--ink);color:#cbd2df}.planner-action strong{color:white}.planner-action p{font-size:.7rem}.planner-action .btn{flex:0 0 auto}.disclaimer{margin-top:1rem}@media(max-width:700px){.allocation-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.funnel{grid-template-columns:1fr}.funnel i{transform:rotate(90deg);text-align:center}.planner-action{align-items:stretch;flex-direction:column}}
</style>
